OL,3,C'They were the loudest audience':
OL,4,CBarry Manilow on his British 'Fanilows'
OL,6,FITV News Entertainment Reporter Rishi
OL,7,FDavda sat down with Barry Manilow as
OL,8,Fhe gets ready to end his UK touring
OL,9,Fwith a fortnight residency at the
OL,10,FLondon Palladium
OL,12,FClub, pub, car, waiting room ... it
OL,13,Fdoesn't really matter where you are,
OL,14,Fif 'Copacabana' comes on, you'll be
OL,15,Ftoe-tapping before you know it.
OL,17,FWhether it was an iconic anthem or a
OL,18,Fsentimental ballad, Barry Manilow
OL,19,Fknows how to write a hit - 28 top ten
OL,20,Fsingles is proof of that very
OL,21,Fstatement.
