OL,3,C'They were the loudest audience':
OL,4,CBarry Manilow on his British 'Fanilows'
OL,6,FHe never set out to become a popstar,
OL,7,Fbut that's how things played out,
OL,8,Fbringing a 34-year-old unknown to the
OL,9,FLondon Palladium in 1978.
OL,11,FIt's fair to say that fan's took to
OL,12,Fhim immediately. Barry remembers
OL,13,FBritish fans as "louder than any other
OL,14,Faudience".
