OL,3,C'They were the loudest audience':
OL,4,CBarry Manilow on his British 'Fanilows'
OL,6,F"Everybody tells me at this age, how
OL,7,Fcome I am still running around and
OL,8,Fsinging the high Fs? I don't know, I
OL,9,Fjust think it's gotten old for me now.
OL,10,FI'm done with touring, but I'll keep
OL,11,Fmaking records."
OL,13,FThe 80-year-old has an exceptional
OL,14,Ftrack record when it comes to 'making
OL,15,Frecords.'
