OL,3,C'They were the loudest audience':
OL,4,CBarry Manilow on his British 'Fanilows'
OL,6,FHe's sold more than 85 million albums,
OL,7,Fsongs like 'Mandy, Could it be Magic
OL,8,Fand Looks like we made it,' were all
OL,9,Ffrom the heart, Manilow was known for
OL,10,Fcalling on people's emotions in his
OL,11,Fmusic.
OL,13,FHowever, there was one song that
OL,14,Fwasn't particularly soaked in feelings
OL,15,F'Copacabana' was a surprise success.
OL,16,FHe laughs while reflecting how "it
OL,17,Fwasn't full of emotion".
