OL,3,C'They were the loudest audience':
OL,4,CBarry Manilow on his British 'Fanilows'
OL,6,F"It was the cleverest, catchiest song
OL,7,Fwe had ever written. And we thought it
OL,8,Fwas a novelty cut on that album and
OL,9,Fnobody would ever hear it. And that
OL,10,Fwas the biggest surprise."
OL,12,FThe New York native has broken records
OL,13,Fin Las Vegas for more residency
OL,14,Fperformances than the late, great
OL,15,FElvis Presley.
OL,17,FTravelling the world, loved by
OL,18,Fmillions of adoring fans, it was a
OL,19,Fmoment in the UK that provided his
OL,20,Ffondest career memory.
