OL,3,C'They were the loudest audience':
OL,4,CBarry Manilow on his British 'Fanilows'
OL,6,F"The moment was meeting Princess
OL,7,FDiana. I meet Diana and Charles
OL,8,Fbackstage at the Royal Festival Hall.
OL,9,FEverything's royal around here.
OL,11,F"She was a fan and she couldn't even
OL,12,Flook at me. I'll never forget that,
OL,13,Fshe was beautiful," he adds.
OL,15,FBarry Manilow's 14-night residency
OL,16,Fstarts on Thursday 23rd May at the
OL,17,FLondon Palladium.
